name: Json.Viewer
comment: @docs Model, Msg, init, view, update, updateValue

types.name: Model
Msg
types.comment:
Local messages of Json.Viewer component. Usage example:

    type Msg
        = JsonViewerMsg Json.Viewer.Msg
        | {- ...the rest of your app messages -}

values.name: init
update
values.comment:
Toggle expandable node. Usage example:

    update msg model =
        case msg of
            JsonViewerMsg m ->
                { model
                    | jsonViewer =
                        model.jsonViewer |> update m
                } ! []

            {- ...the rest of your app message handling -}

values.name: updateValue
values.comment: Helper to update value without re-initializing the whole component

values.name: view
values.comment:
Render JsonViewer. Usage example:

    view: Model -> Html Msg
    view model=
        model.jsonViewer
            |> Json.Viewer.view
            |> Html.map JsonViewerMsg
